Notes: 1. It is clear that Justice Steward went to school in Melbourne, but is unclear as to whether he lived there. In his ceremonial welcome to the court, Christian Porter notes how Steward went to Xavier College in Melbourne. Later, however, he recalls how, when he was 12, Steward went on a "trip into Melbourne", seemingly indicating that he was not residing their already.
